00:22:22.169 --> 00:22:28.750
tried my best to make the contemporary views
of the neighborhood look beautiful using color,

00:22:28.750 --> 00:22:35.409
et cetera. And this was not to gloss over
anything in terms of what happens in the neighborhood.

00:22:35.409 --> 00:22:41.720
What it's for is because I feel like its beauty
there in order to actually better serve the

00:22:41.720 --> 00:22:46.480
people who live there and also beauty as a,
as a metaphor.

00:22:46.480 --> 00:22:52.720
Like in this case, up high, I put a lot of
golden colors, et cetera on those free things

00:22:52.720 --> 00:22:57.380
in nature that we can always appreciate like
the way the light hits a building in the sunset

00:22:57.380 --> 00:23:03.770
and below I missed the pavement. The beauty,
the color comes entirely from the people themselves

00:23:03.770 --> 00:23:08.159
which is what I actually found and there's
precious little infrastructure to support

00:23:08.159 --> 00:23:11.080
that – them.

00:23:11.080 --> 00:23:17.059
And as for the past, you know I always show
the past as well - instead of showing a separate

00:23:17.059 --> 00:23:24.169
panel for the past, this time I made these
little vapor like, sort of like smoky things,

00:23:24.169 --> 00:23:29.250
that drift up from the various locations where
I want to mention something that used to be

00:23:29.250 --> 00:23:30.250
there before.

00:23:30.250 --> 00:23:33.330
And they're kind of like - I call them the
'ghosts of the past' and sort of, they drift

00:23:33.330 --> 00:23:40.610
up towards symbols of, of the things that
used to be there. So all of these buildings,

00:23:40.610 --> 00:23:45.840
et cetera, there actually used to be in these
various parking lots. Really a lot of great

00:23:45.840 --> 00:23:50.000
theatres, et cetera have been torn down to
make room for parking lots and the great Black

00:23:50.000 --> 00:23:52.680
Hawk Jazz Club, legendary place, was torn
down.

00:23:52.680 --> 00:23:56.080
There's a parking lot there. So there's a
lot of - I found the parking lots and like

00:23:56.080 --> 00:24:05.350
